title: Episode 31 - Emma Lincoln-Smith Interview (Brink Vault 2011)
itunes:title: Episode 31 - Emma Lincoln-Smith Interview (Brink Vault 2011)
description: Taking you back to 2011 with another 'vault' interview today as we chat with Australian Skeleton racer Emma Lincoln-Smith. From the amazing way she found herself in the sport right through to the perils and danger and excitement it brings, Emma gives on of our most entertaining vault interviews yet!
